title: REPLAY w/ Rose Rollins

description:
Original Air Date: April 14, 2021


PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey.

Produced by Melisa D. Monts

 

Kate and Leisha are joined by friend and former co-star Rose Rollins to catch up, talk about her new project, and answer listener questions.



Follow us on Twitter @ThePantsPod

Follow us on Instagram ThePantsPod

Email us: kateandleisha@gmail.com

Music: Carol Parra @csssuxxx

Artwork: Lovefoxxx
